The port the admin interface of an OpenTTD server is listening on. Please note that OpenTTD will not start a listener on this port when [[en/Archive/Manual/Settings/Admin password]] is not set.
The interface this port will be listened on can be defined with the [[en/Server bind addresses]] setting. If this is not set it will listen on localhost by default.

More information on the admin interface can be found here: http://svn.openttd.org/trunk/docs/admin_network.txt

== Config ==
'''Valid options:''' [Valid [http://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Port_(computer_networking) port] number 0-65535]

'''Default:''' 3977

Example with default port set:
<pre>
[network]
server_admin_port = 3977
</pre>

